An iconic rendering of the fleur de lis.  Feast your eyes on this unique abstract aromatherapy infused pendant/locket necklace and showcase your artistic side. Created in a flattering tear drop shape.  It's the perfect jewelry addition for you or as a wonderful gift. 

 

It is made out of 316L stainless steel (hypoallergenic metal) and includes a 24" chain and five tear drop shaped felt pads.  Just add a few drops of your favorite essential oil to the felt pad and place in the pendant with an easy magnetic open and close access.  We offer a variety of scents for you to choose from to get you or your gift recipient started.  Enjoy!

We are located in the USA and offer a great assortment of essential oil pieces to consider.  Please check out our store for more.

Includes:

  • 24" 'O' Chain Necklace
  • 316L Stainless Steel Locket
  • One (1) dram filled essential oil scent of choice
  • Five (5) felt pads (black, white & pink)
  • Black Felt Bag
  • Total Senses Box
